* bug_found_avp_floating_point.txt contains vectors that found bugs either
in ISS or in RTL simulation.

* tests_avp_floating_point.txt contains generated vectors from testfloat
and Flopoco.

Only tests_avp_floating_point.txt is used to generate avps so
bug_found_avp_floating_point.txt should be appended to the end of
tests_avp_floating_point.txt when new vectors are generated.
